                    <li><a href="/articles/bc-pnp-job-offer-requirements-2026" class="text-green-600 hover:underline">BC PNP Job Offer Requirements 2026</a> — What your employer's offer letter must include</li>
                    <li><a href="/articles/bc-pnp-after-nomination" class="text-green-600 hover:underline">After Nomination: Next Steps</a> — What to do once you receive your provincial nomination</li>
                </ul>
